<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-09 09:08 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0167 &Cx1f; tad-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NEWS-QUESTIONS10-TAKE     12-09 1671
