<HEADLINE>
FLEDGLING CHURCHES ARE RELIGIOUS NOMADS
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By TARA DOOLEY 
c.1998 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
