   FBN-CHANDLER _ ATLANTA _ Chris Chandler, knocked out of the game
earlier this year in a game vs. the Saints, continues to take
pounding with five sacks vs. Colts. And the Saints blitzed the
Cowboys into submission on Sunday. Concern rules. (Winkeljohn,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 15-18.
