Ruff abandons his customary behind-the-scenes approach to wage a
public campaign to sidetrack House Judiciary Committee preparations
to vote articles of impeachment against President Clinton. Ruff,
59, tells the panel that the president is ``looking for an end to
this process'' with a congressional vote of censure. By STEWART M.
POWELL. (Already filed.)
</P>
