 &UR; PERSONAL TECHNOLOGY &QL;  &LR; 
 &UR;  &QL;  &LR; 
 &UR; MOUSE _ &LR;  It's December 1968. Lyndon Johnson is president, the
Grateful Dead is performing at Winterland and computers are giant
