 This ``separate buy'' article is from Latin Trade magazine,
America's leading journal of Latin American business, finance and
trade: &HT;    CANAL FEVER. Some businessmen expect a gold rush after the
Panama Canal changes hands from U.S. to Panamanian authorities in
1999. Will the Panama-owned canal win or will others in the region
reap the benefits of a growing shipping business?
