<HEADLINE>
DETOUR ON THE ROAD TO
 DAMASCUS
</HEADLINE>
  (For use by N.Y. Times News Service
 clients) 
 By E.J. MONTINI 
 c.1998 The Arizona Republic 
<TEXT>
<P>
   After James Hamm got dumped by the invertebrates running Arizona
State University, I decided to look around for a profession that
wouldn't automatically reject an ar ticulate man with degrees from
