<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-09 23:53 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2202 &Cx1f; tic-z
r a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-PREZNEXT-AZR &LR;      12-09 0674
